'''丹尼爾·班尼特·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|Daniel Bennett Smith}}，{{bd|1956年|3月6日}}），[[美國|美國]]外交官，現任{{link-en|美國外交學院|Foreign Service Institute}}院長，自2018年9月起獲總統提名及參議院通過為{{link-en|美國外交體系職業大使|United States Foreign Service Career Ambassador}}層級官員，即最高級別的外交官。<ref name="Training">{{cite news|date=2018-10-26|title=Training center for U.S. diplomats gets a new director|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/training-center-for-us-diplomats-gets-a-new-director/2018/10/26/ebb58cfe-443e-40e6-8676-14ec813e5311_story.html|accessdate=2018-10-27|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412141856/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/training-center-for-us-diplomats-gets-a-new-director/2018/10/26/ebb58cfe-443e-40e6-8676-14ec813e5311_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

丹尼爾於2014年至2018年間任職[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]{{link-en|情報研究助理國務卿|Assistant Secretary of State for Intelligence and Research}}<ref name="DOSBIO">{{cite news |url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/225045.htm |title=Daniel B. Smith |publisher=[[美國國務院|美國國務院]] |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2017-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002183228/https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/225045.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並被美國外交界視為資深外交官。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/26/magazine/mike-pompeo-translates-trump.html|title=Mike Pompeo's Mission: Translate Trump to a Wary World|last=Schwartz|first=Mattathias|date=2019-02-26|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|access-date=2019-02-26|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2019-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921073516/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/26/magazine/mike-pompeo-translates-trump.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年1月20日中午，在新任總統[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]的[[2021年美國總統就職典禮|就職典禮]]及前任國務卿[[麥克·龐培歐|麥克·龐培歐]]離任之後，史密斯被任命為代理國務卿<ref>{{Cite web|last=Press|first=The Associated|date=2021-01-20|title=New acting secretary of state is career diplomat|url=https://okcfox.com/news/nation-world/new-acting-secretary-of-state-is-career-diplomat|access-date=2021-01-20|website=KOKH|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128194343/https://okcfox.com/news/nation-world/new-acting-secretary-of-state-is-career-diplomat|dead-url=no}}</ref>，代理任期至同月26日為止。

== 早年生活 ==
史密斯在[[科羅拉多大學波德分校|科羅拉多大學波德分校]]獲得文學士學位後繼續深造，之後獲得[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]文學碩士和哲學博士學位。<ref name="DOSBIO"/><ref>{{cite news |quote=After fulfilling his award-winning duties as a career officer in the Senior Foreign Service, Daniel Bennett Smith (Hist’77) has served as U.S. ambassador to Greece since September. Before this role, he served as executive secretary of the State Department. |title=Class Notes – March 2011 |date=01-03-2011 |url=http://www.coloradanmagazine.org/2011/03/01/class-notes-march-2011/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602034308/http://www.coloradanmagazine.org/2011/03/01/class-notes-march-2011/ |archive-date=2017-06-02 |publisher=The Alumni Association of the University of Colorado Boulder |accessdate=2021-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其博士論文題目為《走向國際主義：1933年至1939年的[[羅斯福新政|新政]]對外經濟政策》，並於1983年完成。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://archive.org/details/doubleedgeddiplo00pete |quote=Daniel Bennett Smith stanford. |page=[https://archive.org/details/doubleedgeddiplo00pete/page/202 202] |title=Double-edged Diplomacy: International Bargaining and Domestic Politics |publisher=[[加州大學出版社|加州大學出版社]] |isbn=9780520076815 |year=1993 |editor-first=Peter B. |editor-last=Evans |editor-first2=Harold Karan |editor-last2=Jacobson |editor-first3=Robert D. |editor-last3=Putnam}}</ref>

== 職業生涯 ==
史密斯曾擔任美國國務院執行官、領事事務首席副部長及國務院副執行官等職。他亦曾於[[瑞士|瑞士]][[伯恩|伯恩]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦堡]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]][[渥太華|渥太華]]及[[瑞典|瑞典]][[斯德哥爾摩|斯德哥爾摩]]等地任外交官，亦曾在[[美國空軍學院|美國空軍學院]]教授政治學。<ref name="BIO">{{cite news|date=2021-01-21|title=Daniel B. Smith ACTING SECRETARY OF STATE|work=美國國務院|url=https://www.state.gov/biographies/daniel-b-smith/|access-date=2021-01-21|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120203111/https://www.state.gov/biographies/daniel-b-smith/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

史密斯在[[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]在任總統時期，於2010年至2013年擔任美國駐[[希臘|希臘]]大使。<ref>{{cite news |title=Daniel Bennett Smith (1956–) |quote=Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary (Greece) Appointed: August 8, 2010 Presentation of Credentials: September 28, 2010 Termination of Mission: Left post on August 5, 2013 |url=https://history.state.gov/departmenthistory/people/smith-daniel-bennett |author=Office of the Historian |author-link=Office of the Historian |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602020059/https://history.state.gov/departmenthistory/people/smith-daniel-bennett |archive-date=2017-06-02 |accessdate=2021-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年末，由於史密斯長期與情報界密切合作，擁有監督及協調情報與執法活動的經驗，因而獲奧巴馬及時任國務卿[[約翰·福布斯·克里|約翰·凱瑞]]提名史密斯擔任情報研究助理國務卿。<ref>{{cite news|date=2013-12-17|title=Statement of Daniel Bennett Smith Nominee for Assistant Secretary of State for Intelligence and Research Senate Select Committee on Intelligence|work=|url=https://www.intelligence.senate.gov/sites/default/files/hearings/smith.pdf|access-date=2021-01-21|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220203454/https://www.intelligence.senate.gov/sites/default/files/hearings/smith.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>他於2014年至2018年間為情報研究助理國務卿，並於2018年10月獲委任為美國外交學院院長。<ref name="BIO" />

2021年1月，新任總統拜登選擇史密斯擔任代理國務卿，任期至[[美國參議院|參議院]]通過[[安東尼·布林肯|安東尼·布林肯]]的提名為止。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-biden-state-smith/daniel-smith-appointed-acting-u-s-secretary-of-state-idUSKBN29P2OP|title=Daniel Smith appointed acting U.S. secretary of state|date=2020-01-20|accessdate=2020-01-21|work=[[路透社|路透社]]|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207000123/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-biden-state-smith/daniel-smith-appointed-acting-u-s-secretary-of-state-idUSKBN29P2OP|dead-url=no}}</ref>

